!!! Connecting remotely

!!! Experimental code

In your inspect window (Inspector on a PotRemoteBoard), let's initialize the led and set the pin GPI026 to be in PWM output mode as we did in the last lesson:

[[[
led := gpio26.
led bePWMOutput.
]]]


Try to change the fading of the LED like that:

[[[
led writePWMValue: aValue
]]]

aValue could be between 0 and 1023.
Try to wrote a program that will fade the LED progressively from on to off.

